            <div class="prose-lg">
              <p>
                Founded in 2015, Bright Future Foundation began with a simple belief: that education is the most
                powerful tool for creating lasting positive change in communities. What started as a small tutoring
                program in a single neighborhood has grown into a comprehensive network of educational initiatives
                serving thousands of learners across multiple regions.
              </p>
              <p>
                Our approach is rooted in partnership and respect. We work closely with local communities to
                understand their unique needs and co-create solutions that are sustainable and culturally relevant.
                From early childhood literacy programs to adult vocational training, we're committed to supporting
                learners at every stage of their journey.
              </p>
